---
title: Progress Button
description: A button that animates a fill on click using a checkbox and `background-size` — pure CSS state machine.
slug: progress-button
cssFile: progress-button.css
explanation: "A hidden checkbox is the state machine. When checked, `::before` animates from `scaleX(0)` to `scaleX(1)` with `transform-origin: left` — this creates the left-to-right fill. Three label spans (idle, loading, done) swap visibility using `@keyframes` with `animation-delay`, so the text transitions happen at the right points in the 2-second fill animation."
---
{% extends "example.njk" %}
{% block demo %}
<div class="demo-progress-button">
	<div class="prog-group">
		<input type="checkbox" id="prog-1" class="prog-input">
		<label for="prog-1" class="prog-btn">
			<span class="prog-idle">▶ Run build</span>
			<span class="prog-loading">Building…</span>
			<span class="prog-done">✓ Complete</span>
		</label>
		<span class="prog-hint">click to start</span>
	</div>
	<div class="prog-group">
		<input type="checkbox" id="prog-2" class="prog-input">
		<label for="prog-2" class="prog-btn">
			<span class="prog-idle">↑ Deploy</span>
			<span class="prog-loading">Deploying…</span>
			<span class="prog-done">✓ Live</span>
		</label>
		<span class="prog-hint">click to start</span>
	</div>
</div>
{% endblock %}

{% block html_code %}
{%- highlight "html" %}
<input type="checkbox" id="prog-1" class="prog-input">
<label for="prog-1" class="prog-btn">
  <span class="prog-idle">▶ Run build</span>
  <span class="prog-loading">Building…</span>
  <span class="prog-done">✓ Complete</span>
</label>
{%- endhighlight %}
{% endblock %}

{% block css_code %}
{%- highlight "css" %}
.prog-btn {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.prog-btn::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: var(--accent);
  transform: scaleX(0);
  transform-origin: left;
}

.prog-input:checked ~ .prog-btn::before {
  animation: prog-fill 2s ease-in-out forwards;
}

.prog-input:checked ~ .prog-btn .prog-idle {
  animation: prog-fade-out .2s forwards;
}

.prog-input:checked ~ .prog-btn .prog-done {
  animation: prog-fade-in .2s 2s forwards;
}

@keyframes prog-fill {
  to { transform: scaleX(1); }
}
{%- endhighlight %}
{% endblock %}
